                <h1>Quick Guide: Change Background Color on Instagram Stories</h1>
                <p>Changing the background color of your Instagram Story is easy! Start by creating a new story and tapping the drawing tool or the text tool. Select the pen icon, choose your desired color from the palette, then tap and hold on the screen until the background changes to that color. You can also use gradient options for a trendy look!</p>
